      <title>墨西哥新国家航空公司因 8 亿美元合同纠纷被起诉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/mexico-s-new-state-airline-sued-in-800-million-contract-dispute</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥新成立的国有航空公司被政府雇佣来管理飞机租赁和雇用机组人员的公司起诉，声称该航空公司缺乏合作，使整个企业陷入危险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/mexico-s-new-state-airline-sued-in-800-million-contract-dispute</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 21:41:36 GMT</pubDate>
